   "source": [
    "# 文本摘要（Seq2Seq Summarization）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "本文我们将运用 Transformers 库来完成文本摘要任务。文本摘要同样是一个 Seq2Seq 任务，旨在尽可能保留文本语义的情况下将长文本压缩为短文本。\n",
    "\n",
    "## 1.1 数据来源与核心任务\n",
    "\n",
    "数据来源：爬取自中国主流社交媒体平台——新浪微博。\n",
    "\n",
    "核心任务：根据一段较长的短文本（通常是微博的正文内容），生成一句极其精炼的摘要（通常是用户在发布微博时自己写的、带有概括性质的短句或标题）。\n",
    "\n",
    "## 1.2 数据集的三个核心部分（结构划分）\n",
    "\n",
    "为了保证数据规模与评测的严谨性，作者将数据集在**物理上**划分为三个部分。但在真实的工程应用中，Part II 和 Part III 必须经过**人工打分（1-5分）的逻辑过滤**才能使用。\n",
    "\n",
    "**评分标准（可用性水位线）：**\n",
    "* **1-2分**：与原文无关，或存在事实性错误/关键信息缺失（**脏数据，必须丢弃**）。\n",
    "* **3分**：抓住了部分核心内容，但在流畅度或全面性上略有瑕疵（可用边缘）。\n",
    "* **4-5分**：高度相关，完美概括核心内容，语句通顺（**优质金标准数据**）。\n",
    "\n",
    "**具体结构与可用规模对齐表：**\n",
    "\n",
    "| 数据集切分 | 物理总规模 | 真实可用规模 (Score ≥ 3) | 数据特点与工程用途 |\n",
    "| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |\n",
    "| **Part I (训练集)** | 约 2,400,591 条 | 全量使用 (需自行清洗) | **海量但带噪**。直接从微博抓取，自动配对。主要用于模型的大规模预训练或 SFT（监督微调）阶段的基础能力灌输。 |\n",
    "| **Part II (验证集)** | 10,666 条 | **约 8,685 条** | **人工打分验证**。用于训练过程中的超参数调优与 Loss 验证，防止过拟合。 |\n",
    "| **Part III (测试集)** | 1,106 条 | **约 725 条** | **高质量人工精标**。专门用于最终评估模型性能的测试基准（Benchmark）。 |\n",
    "\n",
    "*(⚠️ 避坑指南：在写 DataLoader 评测模型时，必须硬编码 `if score < 3: continue` 的逻辑。如果用全量 Part III 跑 ROUGE 指标，分数会显著异常并偏低。)*\n",
    "\n",
    "## 1.3 数据格式与示例\n",
    "\n",
    "数据通常以 tsv 形式提供，每行格式为 `摘要!=!正文`。\n",
    "\n",
    "输入文本 (Source Text):\n",
    "> 日前，方舟子发文直指林志颖旗下爱碧丽推销假保健品，引起哗然。对此，林志颖方面不仅拒绝承认，还表示将起诉方舟子。不过，这似乎并没能打消大众的疑虑。昨日，又有媒体爆出，爱碧丽不仅属于无厂房无研发的"皮包公司"，而且林志颖的"逆生长"也并非是因为服用了该产品。\n",
    "\n",
    "目标摘要 (Target Summary):\n",
    "> 林志颖公司被疑是"皮包公司" 逆生长谎言遭戳穿\n",
    "\n",
    "## 1.4 数据特点与工程挑战\n",
    "\n",
    "在实际使用 LCSTS 进行模型训练或评测时，会面临以下几个典型的工程难点：\n",
    "\n",
    "- **极强的口语化与社交媒体噪声**：微博数据充斥着网络流行语、颜文字、错别字、@某人、#话题标签# 以及各种链接。\n",
    "- **强烈的生成式（Abstractive）特征**：微博的摘要往往是用户自己概括的，包含原文中没有的新词汇，要求模型具备真正的语义理解和生成能力。\n",
    "- **信息压缩率高**：原文通常在 100 字左右，而摘要往往被限制在 10-20 字以内。\n",
    "\n",
    "## 1.5 当前大模型时代的价值\n",
    "\n",
    "在目前的 LLM 时代，LCSTS 的角色发生了一些转变：\n",
    "\n",
    "- 它很少再被用来从头训练一个小模型，而是经常被混入大语言模型的 SFT（指令微调）语料库中，用来增强模型对中文短文本的总结概括能力。\n",
    "- Part III（高质量测试集）依然被广泛用作评估 LLM 中文文本摘要能力的基准测试之一，常用的评估指标依然是 ROUGE（ROUGE-1, ROUGE-2, ROUGE-L）。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 1: 导入工具包\n",
    "import torch\n",
    "from torch import nn\n",
    "from torch.utils.data import Dataset, DataLoader\n",
    "from torch.optim import AdamW\n",
    "from transformers import AutoTokenizer, AutoModelForSeq2SeqLM, AutoConfig, get_scheduler\n",
    "from rouge import Rouge\n",
    "from tqdm.auto import tqdm\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 2: 数据集 LCSTS\n",
    "class LCSTS(Dataset):\n",
    "    def __init__(self, data_file, max_size=None):\n",
    "        self.data = self.load_data(data_file, max_size)\n",
    "\n",
    "    def load_data(self, data_file, max_size):\n",
    "        Data = {}\n",
    "        with open(data_file, 'rt', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n",
    "            for idx, line in enumerate(f):\n",
    "                if max_size and idx >= max_size:\n",
    "                    break\n",
    "                items = line.strip().split('!=!')\n",
    "                if len(items) != 2:\n",
    "                    continue\n",
    "                Data[idx] = {'title': items[0], 'content': items[1]}\n",
    "        return Data\n",
    "\n",
    "    def __len__(self):\n",
    "        return len(self.data)\n",
    "\n",
    "    def __getitem__(self, idx):\n",
    "        return self.data[idx]\n",
    "\n",
    "train_data = LCSTS('../../data/lcsts_tsv/data1.tsv', max_size=200000)\n",
    "valid_data = LCSTS('../../data/lcsts_tsv/data2.tsv')\n",
    "test_data  = LCSTS('../../data/lcsts_tsv/data3.tsv')\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'Train: {len(train_data)}, Valid: {len(valid_data)}, Test: {len(test_data)}')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 3: 加载分词器\n",
    "MODEL_CHOICE = \"csebuetnlp/mT5_multilingual_XLSum\"\n",
    "tokenizer = AutoTokenizer.from_pretrained(MODEL_CHOICE)\n",
    "\n",
    "sample = \"我叫张三，在苏州大学学习计算机。\"\n",
    "print(tokenizer.convert_ids_to_tokens(tokenizer(sample).input_ids))\n",
    "# mT5 使用 SentencePiece (Unigram)，特殊符号 ▁ 表示词首"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 4: 数据样本预览\n",
    "for i in range(3):\n",
    "    sample = train_data[i]\n",
    "    print(f\"[Title]   {sample['title']}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"[Content] {sample['content']}\")\n",
    "    print()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 5: 超参数配置\n",
    "class Args:\n",
    "    model_checkpoint = MODEL_CHOICE\n",
    "    max_input_length  = 512\n",
    "    max_target_length = 64\n",
    "    batch_size    = 4\n",
    "    learning_rate = 1e-5\n",
    "    epoch_num     = 3\n",
    "    num_beams     = 4\n",
    "    warmup_ratio  = 0.1\n",
    "\n",
    "    if torch.backends.mps.is_available():\n",
    "        device = torch.device(\"mps\")\n",
    "    elif torch.cuda.is_available():\n",
    "        device = torch.device(\"cuda\")\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        device = torch.device(\"cpu\")\n",
    "\n",
    "args = Args()\n",
    "print(f'Using {args.device} device')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 6: 构建模型\n",
    "# tie_word_embeddings=False：encoder/decoder 的 embedding 权重不共享，对中文效果更好\n",
    "model = AutoModelForSeq2SeqLM.from_pretrained(\n",
    "    args.model_checkpoint, tie_word_embeddings=False\n",
    ")\n",
    "model = model.to(args.device)\n",
    "print(f'Model parameters: {sum(p.numel() for p in model.parameters()):,}')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 7: 构建数据加载器\n",
    "def get_dataLoader(dataset, tokenizer, model, args, shuffle=False):\n",
    "    def collote_fn(batch_samples):\n",
    "        batch_inputs  = [s['content'] for s in batch_samples]\n",
    "        batch_targets = [s['title']   for s in batch_samples]\n",
    "\n",
    "        batch_data = tokenizer(\n",
    "            batch_inputs,\n",
    "            padding=True,\n",
    "            max_length=args.max_input_length,\n",
    "            truncation=True,\n",
    "            return_tensors=\"pt\"\n",
    "        )\n",
    "        labels = tokenizer(\n",
    "            batch_targets,\n",
    "            padding=True,\n",
    "            max_length=args.max_target_length,\n",
    "            truncation=True,\n",
    "            return_tensors=\"pt\"\n",
    "        )[\"input_ids\"]\n",
    "\n",
    "        # teacher forcing：将标签右移一位作为 decoder 的输入\n",
    "        batch_data['decoder_input_ids'] = model.prepare_decoder_input_ids_from_labels(labels)\n",
    "        # EOS 之后的 padding 不计入损失\n",
    "        end_token_index = torch.where(labels == tokenizer.eos_token_id)[1]\n",
    "        for idx, end_idx in enumerate(end_token_index):\n",
    "            labels[idx][end_idx + 1:] = -100\n",
    "        batch_data['labels'] = labels\n",
    "        return batch_data\n",
    "\n",
    "    return DataLoader(dataset, batch_size=args.batch_size, shuffle=shuffle, collate_fn=collote_fn)\n",
    "\n",
    "train_dataloader = get_dataLoader(train_data, tokenizer, model, args, shuffle=True)\n",
    "valid_dataloader = get_dataLoader(valid_data, tokenizer, model, args)\n",
    "test_dataloader  = get_dataLoader(test_data,  tokenizer, model, args)\n",
    "print(f'Train batches: {len(train_dataloader)}, Valid: {len(valid_dataloader)}, Test: {len(test_dataloader)}')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 8: 批次数据预览\n",
    "batch = next(iter(train_dataloader))\n",
    "print('Keys:', list(batch.keys()))\n",
    "print('Shapes:', {k: v.shape for k, v in batch.items()})"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 9: 优化器与学习率调度器\n",
    "no_decay = ['bias', 'LayerNorm.weight']\n",
    "optimizer_grouped_parameters = [\n",
    "    {'params': [p for n, p in model.named_parameters() if not any(nd in n for nd in no_decay)],\n",
    "     'weight_decay': 0.01},\n",
    "    {'params': [p for n, p in model.named_parameters() if any(nd in n for nd in no_decay)],\n",
    "     'weight_decay': 0.0}\n",
    "]\n",
    "optimizer = AdamW(optimizer_grouped_parameters, lr=args.learning_rate)\n",
    "\n",
    "total_steps  = args.epoch_num * len(train_dataloader)\n",
    "warmup_steps = int(args.warmup_ratio * total_steps)\n",
    "lr_scheduler = get_scheduler(\n",
    "    \"linear\",\n",
    "    optimizer=optimizer,\n",
    "    num_warmup_steps=warmup_steps,\n",
    "    num_training_steps=total_steps\n",
    ")\n",
    "print(f'Total steps: {total_steps}, Warmup steps: {warmup_steps}')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 10: 训练函数\n",
    "def train_loop(dataloader, model, optimizer, lr_scheduler, epoch, total_loss):\n",
    "    progress_bar = tqdm(range(len(dataloader)))\n",
    "    progress_bar.set_description(f'loss: {0:>7f}')\n",
    "    finish_batch_num = (epoch - 1) * len(dataloader)\n",
    "\n",
    "    model.train()\n",
    "    for step, batch_data in enumerate(dataloader, start=1):\n",
    "        batch_data = batch_data.to(args.device)\n",
    "        outputs = model(**batch_data)\n",
    "        loss = outputs.loss\n",
    "\n",
    "        optimizer.zero_grad()\n",
    "        loss.backward()\n",
    "        optimizer.step()\n",
    "        lr_scheduler.step()\n",
    "\n",
    "        total_loss += loss.item()\n",
    "        progress_bar.set_description(f'loss: {total_loss / (finish_batch_num + step):>7f}')\n",
    "        progress_bar.update(1)\n",
    "    return total_loss"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 11: 测试函数（ROUGE 评估）\n",
    "rouge_metric = Rouge()\n",
    "\n",
    "def test_loop(dataloader, model, tokenizer, args):\n",
    "    all_preds, all_labels = [], []\n",
    "\n",
    "    model.eval()\n",
    "    with torch.no_grad():\n",
    "        for batch_data in tqdm(dataloader):\n",
    "            input_ids      = batch_data['input_ids'].to(args.device)\n",
    "            attention_mask = batch_data['attention_mask'].to(args.device)\n",
    "            labels         = batch_data['labels']\n",
    "\n",
    "            generated_ids = model.generate(\n",
    "                input_ids=input_ids,\n",
    "                attention_mask=attention_mask,\n",
    "                num_beams=args.num_beams,\n",
    "                max_length=args.max_target_length\n",
    "            )\n",
    "            preds = tokenizer.batch_decode(generated_ids, skip_special_tokens=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "            label_ids = labels.clone()\n",
    "            label_ids[label_ids == -100] = tokenizer.pad_token_id\n",
    "            refs = tokenizer.batch_decode(label_ids, skip_special_tokens=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "            for pred, ref in zip(preds, refs):\n",
    "                pred = pred.strip() or \"无\"\n",
    "                ref  = ref.strip()  or \"无\"\n",
    "                all_preds.append(pred)\n",
    "                all_labels.append(ref)\n",
    "\n",
    "    scores = rouge_metric.get_scores(all_preds, all_labels, avg=True)\n",
    "    r1 = scores['rouge-1']['f']\n",
    "    r2 = scores['rouge-2']['f']\n",
    "    rl = scores['rouge-l']['f']\n",
    "    print(f\"ROUGE-1: {r1:.4f}  ROUGE-2: {r2:.4f}  ROUGE-L: {rl:.4f}\")\n",
    "    return (r1 + r2 + rl) / 3"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 12: 训练\n",
    "history = {'train_loss': [], 'valid_rouge': []}\n",
    "best_rouge = 0.\n",
    "best_model_path = 'best_summarization_model.bin'\n",
    "\n",
    "for epoch in range(1, args.epoch_num + 1):\n",
    "    print(f'Epoch {epoch}/{args.epoch_num}')\n",
    "    print('-' * 30)\n",
    "    total_loss = train_loop(train_dataloader, model, optimizer, lr_scheduler, epoch, 0)\n",
    "    history['train_loss'].append(total_loss / len(train_dataloader))\n",
    "\n",
    "    avg_rouge = test_loop(valid_dataloader, model, tokenizer, args)\n",
    "    history['valid_rouge'].append(avg_rouge)\n",
    "\n",
    "    if avg_rouge > best_rouge:\n",
    "        best_rouge = avg_rouge\n",
    "        torch.save(model.state_dict(), best_model_path)\n",
    "        print(f'New best saved! avg ROUGE: {avg_rouge:.4f}')\n",
    "    print()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'Done! Best avg ROUGE: {best_rouge:.4f}')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 13: 绘制训练曲线\n",
    "fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(12, 4))\n",
    "\n",
    "axes[0].plot(range(1, args.epoch_num + 1), history['train_loss'], 'o-')\n",
    "axes[0].set_xlabel('Epoch')\n",
    "axes[0].set_ylabel('Loss')\n",
    "axes[0].set_title('Training Loss')\n",
    "\n",
    "axes[1].plot(range(1, args.epoch_num + 1), history['valid_rouge'], 's-', color='orange')\n",
    "axes[1].set_xlabel('Epoch')\n",
    "axes[1].set_ylabel('Avg ROUGE')\n",
    "axes[1].set_title('Validation ROUGE')\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 14: 加载最优模型\n",
    "model.load_state_dict(torch.load(best_model_path, map_location=args.device))\n",
    "model.eval()\n",
    "print('Best model loaded.')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 15: 预测函数\n",
    "def summarize(content, model, tokenizer, args):\n",
    "    inputs = tokenizer(\n",
    "        content,\n",
    "        max_length=args.max_input_length,\n",
    "        truncation=True,\n",
    "        return_tensors=\"pt\"\n",
    "    ).to(args.device)\n",
    "    with torch.no_grad():\n",
    "        generated_ids = model.generate(\n",
    "            **inputs,\n",
    "            num_beams=args.num_beams,\n",
    "            max_length=args.max_target_length\n",
    "        )\n",
    "    return tokenizer.decode(generated_ids[0], skip_special_tokens=True)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 16: 验证集示例预测\n",
    "for i in range(3):\n",
    "    sample = valid_data[i]\n",
    "    content    = sample['content']\n",
    "    reference  = sample['title']\n",
    "    prediction = summarize(content, model, tokenizer, args)\n",
    "    print(f\"[Content]    {content}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"[Reference]  {reference}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"[Prediction] {prediction}\")\n",
    "    print()"
   ]
  },
  {
